    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "af507211-f83f-4509-b10a-c06606a1bfea",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Tilting At Flaming Windmills",
        "Location": "LOCATION_EDGY_FOX",
        "PublicId": "129003076784",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ff4e6474-22c9-42dd-9ac1-52dd050ca0b7).Image",
        "Description": "Diana wanted me to burn all of these targets alive so I&#39;ve been going in circles looking for more gasoline, but these bikers only brought one barrel! How do they fuel all these motorcycles?\rWell I&#39;m just going to have to use my imagination on what counts as &quot;fire&quot; for this contract.\rAn explosion makes sense, sure. Electricity is kind of like fire? Turns them to a crisp the same, sort of. This poison would definitely burn someone's insides, yeah.\rNo problem, four fiery bikers coming up!",
        "GameVersion": "8.15.0.63",
